resources.string: â€» Measurable cable length (based on CAT 5E) : 10m ~ 200m
- The measurement result may differ from the official measurement length. Please use it as a reference.
- The cable may not be measured if it is shorted arbitrarily or bent excessibely.
"- The cable status and length may not be measured if any product is connected to the cable end. "
"- When measuring more than 200m, connect TG02 and measure it in the TDRC app. "
- Pair Open : Nothing is connected to the cable end.
- Pair Short : The cable end is short-circuited.
- Cross Pair Short : Cables in other pairs are short-circuited.
- Same Pair Short : Cables in same pair are short-circuited.
- Invalid : Cannot be measured due to unknown reason.
